{
  "texts": [
    "and then learn a node-wise classifier over the rows of H node 2 R 22 × 4.",
    "We further decode H node into a logit vector O 2 R 22 with a linear layer before computing the corresponding softmax cross entropy loss.",
    "For shot prediction, which is once again fully invariant (i.e.",
    "reflections do not change the probability of a shot), we can further average the frame-averaged features across all players to get a global graph representation:",
    "and then learn a binary classifier over h graph 2 R 4."
  ]
}